Privacy Policy

This privacy policy explains how our extension handles the personal information of its users.

Information Collection and Use

Our extension collects the email address of its users in order to provide a personalized experience. We do not collect any other personal information.

Information Protection

We take the protection of our users' personal information very seriously. We use secure servers and data encryption to protect the email addresses that we collect.

Opting Out

If you do not want us to collect your email address, you can choose not to use our extension.

Changes to this Privacy Policy

We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will post any changes on this page, so please check back periodically to stay informed about our privacy practices.

